{"article_id":"MCCs7DxY9sE9cM43","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Rep. Lynn Jenkins , R-Kansas , faulted Senate Democrats on Saturday for this week 's hike in student loan interest rates","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"and urged the upper chamber to pass legislation","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that resolves the issue","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"as soon as the holiday recess ends .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"`` For too long , politicians have been in charge","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"of setting these rates ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"and we keep coming back to cliffs and deadlines like this one , ''","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Jenkins said in the GOP weekly address .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"`` Paying for college is difficult enough","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"without all this uncertainty .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"I have two kids in college ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"I know","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"how hard it can be . ''","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"The interest rates on some student loans officially doubled Monday","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"- to 6.8 % from 3.4 % -","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"after the Senate failed to reach a compromise by the July 1 deadline .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"The hike hits about seven million new subsidized Stafford loans this year for middle- and low-income students ,","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"but does not apply to existing loans .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Negotiators are stuck largely on the question","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"of whether to require an overall cap","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"above which interest rates on new loans could not rise .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Top Senate Democrats want a cap in place","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"to protect students","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"if interest rates spike .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"That is at odds with the slightly different proposals from President Barack Obama and various congressional Republicans ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"which are tied to 10-year Treasury bond rates","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and would include charges for administrative costs","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"but would not include caps .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Republicans ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"who prefer a more market-based approach ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"often point out","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"that the White House 's proposal falls more in line with their own .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"`` When President Obama proposed letting the markets set interest rates instead ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"the Republican-led House passed a bill","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"reflecting his plan , ''","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"Jenkins said .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"`` Republicans in the Senate came to the table with similar ideas .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Unfortunately , Senate Democrats attacked the president 's plan ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"refused to work with us ,","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"and allowed this rate hike to take effect ,","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"leaving for the July 4th holiday","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"without passing a solution . ''","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"Senators worked through last week","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to try to reach a deal ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"but lawmakers from both parties ultimately predicted","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"an agreement would not be made in time .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Nevertheless , many of those same senators said","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"they hope to finalize an agreement shortly after the break","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"and have it apply retroactively","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"so students are not hurt by the temporary hike .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Another disagreement centers on whether the legislation is revenue-neutral .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Senate Democrats say","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"the government should not earn any money","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"or pay down the deficit from the loans","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"they provide ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"something","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"that would happen under the other proposals .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"`` Republicans continue to insist","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that we reduce the deficit on the backs of students and middle-class families , ''","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Adam Jentleson , a spokesman for Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid , said a week before the deadline .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":121,"left":0,"right":120,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":73,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":64,"right":72,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":1,"right":63,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":63,"left":62,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":67,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":66,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":65,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":65,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":68,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":11,"right":69,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":77,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":16,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"adversative","nu